Text: "In 2014 its first time I going to singapore for holiday and business but there\
  \ unique moment because I don't know where the place for my business and my map\
  \ on mobile phone was broken. Oh my god so after confused I ask to people about\
  \ direction to Kampung Bugis and the people very kind to company me went to Bugis\
  \ Village. After in Bugis I'm very happy because my friend is my childhood friend.\
  \ Oh ya, I going to Singapore by a plane and get cheap price for the ticket and\
  \ that's going and back.hahaha \nThank you. Maybe this my story about travelling."
